## User Personas
Below, there are some potential user-personas that, to one degree or another, replicate the possible needs behind their use of the website to satisfy their wants.
### Their Roles

#### College Student
**Bio:** Chris is a 19-year-old freshman student specializing in English literature.

**Needs/Goals:** He needs to review several literary works including classical novels, plays, poetry, etc. for his classes.

**Frustrations:** The over-priced books at the bookstore make it far-fetching for him to buy them.

**Scenario 1:** Chris wants to succeed in his classes. He loves all genres of literary, but he could not afford them. He needs an alternative option to acquire cheaper or free books.